[[question id=5]]
 系统 信息

[[answer]]
 查看操作系统版本等：uname
 显示机器的处理器架构：arch
 显示和设置内核参数：sysctl
 查看帮助文档：man
 显示系统日期：date
 系统运行情况：uptime 和 w
[[answer uname=Linux]]
 查看内存情况：free

[[answer uname=Darwin]]
 查看内存情况：
 [[cmd/]] sysctl -a | egrep 'memory|memsize|swap'


[[question id=10]]
 CPU

[[answer]]
 查看CPU相关信息。

[[answer uname=Linux]]
 [[cmd/]] cat /proc/cpuinfo

[[answer uname=Darwin]]
 [[cmd/]] sysctl -a | grep cpu


[[question id=15]]
 物理 CPU 个数

[[answer uname=Linux]]
 [[cmd/]] cat /proc/cpuinfo | grep "physical id" | sort | uniq | wc -l

[[answer uname=Darwin]]
 [[cmd/]] sysctl -n hw.physicalcpu


[[question id=16]]
 CPU 型号

[[answer uname=Linux]]
 [[cmd/]] cat /proc/cpuinfo | grep 'model name' | sort | uniq

[[answer uname=Darwin]]
 [[cmd/]] sysctl -n machdep.cpu.brand_string


[[question id=20]]
 CPU 个数 [逻辑]

[[answer uname=Linux]]
 [[cmd/]] cat /proc/cpuinfo | grep "processor" | wc -l

[[answer uname=Darwin]]
 [[cmd/]] sysctl -n hw.logicalcpu
 [[cmd/]] sysctl -n hw.ncpu


[[question id=30]]
 内存

[[answer]]
 显示内存相关信息。

[[answer uname=Linux]]
